3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fnextplus%2Fmagazine%2Farticle%2F20180524%2F2_589061_0%2F-%E9%BB%91%E5%AE%A2%E7%8F%BE%E8%BA%AB%E7%88%86%E5%85%A7%E5%B9%95-25%E6%AD%B2%E5%BB%A2%E9%9D%92%E8%AE%8A%E9%BB%91%E5%AE%A2-%E8%A6%AA%E8%BF%B0%E5%85%A5%E4%BE%B5%E5%90%84%E6%AC%BE%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1%E7%95%B6%E7%B7%B4%E5%8A%9F&d=P4z59FLyJTqyFyH6MyYIsOI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=66f4d115\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fnextplus%2Fmagazine%2Farticle%2F20180524%2F2_589061_0%2F-%E9%BB%91%E5%AE%A2%E7%8F%BE%E8%BA%AB%E7%88%86%E5%85%A7%E5%B9%95-25%E6%AD%B2%E5%BB%A2%E9%9D%92%E8%AE%8A%E9%BB%91%E5%AE%A2-%E8%A6%AA%E8%BF%B0%E5%85%A5%E4%BE%B5%E5%90%84%E6%AC%BE%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1%E7%95%B6%E7%B7%B4%E5%8A%9F&h=22253a48\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/nextplus/magazine/article/20180524/2_589061_0/-黑客現身爆內幕-25歲廢青變黑客-親述入侵各款系統當練功</a></div>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T03:32:27.000Z","msg":"點解諗到? 諗到未?"},{"pid":"f41554323be3da683d8831b85a5173a8d774a2b3","tid":681255,"uid":61249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T05:23:45.000Z","msg":"垃圾文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e5338ed11d9dc547763a1a08708e6ae0fd886db","tid":681255,"uid":2442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13aa22277c3ca4181f99356ea0b8ba4d4e21fe7b","tid":681255,"uid":1886,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T01:29:46.000Z","msg":"趁總工程師放假，阿風推翻他設計的程式，重新編寫一個，然後放在他的案上。 <br />\n<br />\n公司接納他的方案，第一次，他覺得在社會上存在過價值。 <br />\n<br />\n「不再是捧餐、抹地，做會被人工智能取代的工作。不能說那些工作沒有價值，但是沒有創造的感覺。」<br />\n<br />\n代價是那段日子，每天起床，發現枕頭上有二十多條頭髮，幾乎秃頭。 <br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/25/194451_4a47a0db6e60853dedfcfdf08a5ca249.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F25%2F194451_4a47a0db6e60853dedfcfdf08a5ca249.png&h=37ba10ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">示意圖。</span></div><br />\n<br />\n自此，他找到自己，但也變成一個黑客。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T06:28:00.000Z","msg":"連仔有冇甩頭髮"},{"pid":"dd6fa13ecd6f37d6c6d0b73fb185f724e7ac23fd","tid":681255,"uid":125479,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T07:41:51.000Z","msg":"【黑客現身爆內幕】宅男黑客網絡任我行 <strong>知己竟是一隻貓攬枕</strong>｜壹週刊<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/spot/20180524/589082\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fspot%2F20180524%2F589082&d=P4z59FLyJTqyFyH6MyYIsOI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=d8c23812\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fspot%2F20180524%2F589082&h=05c699e0\" target=\"_blank\">http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/spot/20180524/589082</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>他與中學拍拖的初戀女友分手後，就沒有再拍拖，怕自己每事解釋的長氣性格，嚇怕對方，自己再一次受傷。<br />\n<br />\n很少人能分享他的喜悅，所以朋友也不多，「他們不會明白，成功入侵到一個系統，滿足感有多大。」<br />\n<br />\n朋友邀他行山，望著優美風景，阿風覺得不外如是，「這樣的景色，不是跟電腦熒幕上看到的一樣嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n每日過著模板般的生活，休息工作再工作，很多人覺得他毒不可耐，但他說是為理想奮鬥。<br />\n<br />\n「我最希望可以幫人做到一個安全和穩定的系統，我見過很多保安問題，不想再見到，<br />\n這理想任重道遠，的確很遠、很遠。」<br />\n</strong><br />\n幾撚好笑 睇落似Netsend"},{"pid":"7cc3bd44eae3abb2c8e04dcbe0049af99d3665ae","tid":681255,"uid":122264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T07:47:11.000Z","msg":"好耐之前有個gpa 4 劍橋個IT人就真係奇才"},{"pid":"0f1a4fa221302e84298b801aee052800e47fa12e","tid":681255,"uid":64694,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T07:52:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/28/155208_93d3a5a567ca67ecd98aed6132fa9d51.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F28%2F155208_93d3a5a567ca67ecd98aed6132fa9d51.jpg&h=78de371b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n頭先重以為係佢嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d6532b655340923368f9735927fbdc49b4ee387","tid":681255,"uid":78